<br>
1. DS your pet or use lvl 44 Fire Pet<br>
2. Wait until Fire pet DS himself<br>
3. Send in pet to attack.<br>
4. Wait about 3 seconds or until the pet's life bar drops once.<br>
5. Heal your pet.<br>
6. /assist your pet and open fire with SoS. (Should drop the first one in 2 casts) <br>
7. Heal Pet again.<br>
8. SOS the last BG.<br>
<br>
I was able to take out 3 corners before having to med...Make sure to wait until pet has recovered before taking on the next corner. This allows you to med for a brief min. <br>
